 <h2 id="British Longhair1";>British Longhair</h2>
 <div>
     The British Longhair, also known as the Highlander or Highland Straight, is a longhaired variant of the British Shorthair. Some registries such as TICA recognise it as a distinct breed,[21] others such as the GCCF treat it as a variant of the British Shorthair, which may be referred to as simply 'British'.[22]

     The breed is identical to the British Shorthair aside from its longer and denser coat.
     <a href="British Longhair.aspx"> read more...</a>
