</div>
 </div>
 <h2 id="Russian Blue1";>Russian Blue</h2>
 <div>
     The Russian Blue cat (Russian: Русская голубая кошка, romanized: Russkaya golubaya koshka), commonly referred to as just Russian Blue, is a pedigreed cat breed with solid blue colours that vary from a light shimmering silver to a darker, slate grey. The short, dense coat, which stands out from the body, has been the breed's hallmark for more than a century.
     <a href="Russian Blue.aspx"> read more...</a>
